data.description: First time to market, this Fischer resale in Grant Settlement is a spacious ranch style home with a fully finished walk-out basement. Situated on a flat and usable lot, enjoy your outdoor living with the fully covered deck just off the kitchen. Open floor plan with first floor primary bedroom and laundry. Kitchen is an eat-in and features a large island, shaker cabinets and granite counters. SS appliances included and exhaust vents to outside. HW flooring covers most of the first level and this home features a wheel chair accessible bathroom with roll in level shower. The lower level is perfect for generational living with a full kitchen set up for a lower level apartment with bed/bath.
